text: Managaz () is a rural locality (a village) in Kalmiyarovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 44 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 22 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 12 km from Starokalmiyarovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Managaz
